  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">1 The Information We Collect and Use A Non-Personally Identifiable Information When you visit a Website we may collect certain data that does not tell us specifically who you are This is Non-Personally Identifiable Information It includes things like your Internet Protocol IP address browser type and the last domain you visited before coming to our Website or the domain you go to when you leave It also includes various statistical data such as which pages you visit on our Websites how long you stay on them and what you click</evidence>
